It all breaks down to this. EQ is NOT addicting. People play cause they CHOOSE to not because some force is making them do it. Could I quit EQ. You can bet the farm safely that I can. If I decide my entertainment time is better spent doing something else I would be gone in a Heartbeat. At the moment EQ is still quite fun to me so I see my time spent on EQ as quality entertainment time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uluwina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>luwina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#E9D756>(10/20/02 7:25:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10893.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: @#%$ i would rather have seen a senate hearing</span><hr size=1> ---------------------<br>
